} This function removes the specified working eckey from the hash table and frees the eckey in memory. C usage: int key_id = start_key(false);
eckey* key = find_eckey(key_id);
remove_eckey(key) dogecoin_key_free: void dogecoin_key_free(eckey* eckey)
